snippet.title: Best VGM 1873 - Suikoden - Theme of a Moonlit Night
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation
Suikoden (1995)
Theme of a Moonlit Night
Tappy Iwase, Mayuko Kageshita, Hiroshi Tamawari & Setsu Taniguchi
